body:
PALLAMANO FEMMINILE A2 / ESORDIO VINCENTE PER CINGOLI CHE IN RIMONTA BATTE PADOVA

Cingoli     Cellini Padova  21-19 (9-12)

CINGOLI, 14 ottobre 2018 – Una grintosa Polisportiva Cingoli riesce a rimontare il Cellini Padova e vince la prima giornata del campionato di Serie A2 Femminile di pallamano.

Le ragazze di Analla, nonostante un tempo passato in svantaggio, hanno risalito la china e hanno vinto meritatamente l’incontro.

Nella prima frazione le cose non si erano messe bene…

summary: Russian athletes secure three medals on Day 7 of 2018 Youth Olympics
title: Russian athletes secure three medals on Day 7 of 2018 Youth Olympics
body:
Russian athletes secure three medals on Day 7 of 2018 Youth Olympics

BUENOS AIRES, October 14. /TASS/. Russian athletes won three medals (one gold, one silver and one bronze) during the seventh day of the 2018 Youth Olympic Games in Argentina’s Buenos Aires.

The gold medal was grabbed by gymnast Ksenia Klimenko. Gymnast Sergei Naidin won two more medals: silver in men’s floor exercise and bronze in men’s pommel horse.

The Russian national squad is in the lead of…

summary: Russia’s Nurmagomedov challenges Mayweather, says there’s ‘only one king’ in the jungle
title: Russia’s Nurmagomedov challenges Mayweather, says there’s ‘only one king’ in the jungle
body:
Russia’s Nurmagomedov challenges Mayweather, says there’s ‘only one king’ in the jungle

MOSCOW, October 14. /TASS/. Russian fighter and UFC lightweight champion Khabib Nurmagomedov has called out US boxer Floyd ” Money” Mayweather for a fight.

“In the jungle [there is] only one king, and I’m the king, of course,” Nurmagomedov said in a video message posted by boxing manager DeJuan Blake on Instagram. “Two guys never lose, why not?!”

The Russian, who won all 27 fights, said…
